{{sep11}}
==Translingual==

===Etymology===
From the date September 11 written in numbers according the format used in the [[United States]], which puts the month before the day.

===Alternative spellings===
'''911'''

===Noun===
'''9/11'''

# The [[terrorist]] events of 11th September, 2001.
# A disturbing event which awakens one or ones to the dangers of the world. ''It was her 9/11.''

